INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('10483','4','1066','Enhanced locations manager','h2. Structure of information system\r\n\r\n* Each client have a folder with attached files.\r\n\r\n* Each client\'s location(object) can have:\r\n** attached documents, organized into user-created folders. Attachments can be uploaded/downloaded/renamed, search or filter. \r\nAttributes: \r\n*** file name\r\n*** file size\r\n*** datetime\r\n*** username\r\n** several points (inside or near location). \r\nAttributes\r\n*** name\r\n** several user-defined form templates (maybe connected with products).\r\nAttributes:\r\n*** name\r\n*** start date - start of current form fill\r\n*** frequency - when start next form fill. Next form fill starts independent of *** Can have several columns. \r\nColumn attributes:\r\n**** header text (label)\r\n**** type: static text, checkmark or input value\r\n**** value: static text or preset value.\r\n** forms list. \r\nForms attributes:\r\n*** form name (by template)\r\n*** fill in (last save) date\r\n*** state (planned, not filled, incomplete, completed)\r\n*** filled values/checkmarks\r\n** several assigned users from list of ERP users. Also guest accounts for clients. But probably just another users group with very limited access.\r\n\r\nform filling expired when new occurence starts (for weekly frequency - the day before next occurence)\r\nform filling repeats until form is deleted.\r\ntemplate should have predefined column with point name. Probably not show in template create/edit, add automatically.\r\nform will have fixed number of rows: 1 for each location.\r\n\r\nh2. Interface\r\nPending\r\n\r\n','2011-02-28',NULL,'5',NULL,'3',NULL,'990','18','2011-01-26 05:55:13','2011-07-14 01:19:09',NULL,'0','40',NULL,'10483','1','2','0');
