INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('21844','2','2379','Add status \'Unavailable\' for users','An user will get the status \'Unavailable\' based on the days/hours set they can work, according to issue #21842\r\n\r\nSo if for example wednesday is not enabled, and today is wednesday, the whole wednesday it will keep this status \'unavailable\'. Status \'Sick\' and \'Holiday\' has always priority above this status \'unavailable\'.',NULL,NULL,'5','1561','7',NULL,'1561','2','2011-06-28 05:58:31','2011-07-03 01:52:28','2011-06-28','0',NULL,NULL,'21844','1','2','0');
INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('21845','2','2379','Planning: Add checkbox \'Show unavailable\' workers','So we will add a checkbox (ticker) to enable/disable the display of \'unavailable\' workers. Based on the issue #21842 where they can set if they work on that day or not. \r\n\r\n_Sometimes it happens accidently that a worker, even if its set in their profile that they don\'t work on some day, they will need to work on the disabled day. Usually this is verbally communicated between worker and manager. But they don\'t want to change the settings all the time, just if they one time need to work on a disabled day for that worker._',NULL,NULL,'5','1561','7',NULL,'1561','4','2011-06-28 06:02:40','2011-07-03 01:52:28','2011-06-28','0',NULL,NULL,'21845','1','2','0');
INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('21846','2','2379','Cashregister: Step 7: Round up values of deposit value (for in enveloppe)','Right now on step 7 it will show in blue, the ammount wich has to be deposited. This value must be round up in steps of 5. So if we have value off \'273,49\' it will become \'275\'. If we have value \'342,33\' it will become \'340\'.',NULL,NULL,'5','1561','7',NULL,'1561','5','2011-06-28 06:06:04','2011-07-03 01:52:29','2011-06-28','0',NULL,NULL,'21846','1','2','0');
