INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('25523','2','2379','V&D shops Cashregister','Cashregister:\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n- Step 1 till 3 has no changes\r\n\r\n\r\nStep 4. Only show following fields:\r\n\r\n- Total turnover\r\n\r\n- Number of paying customers\r\n\r\n- Coupons\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nStep 5 - We don\'t need.\r\n\r\n\r\nStep 6 - Bonus. The V&D shops use the \'old\' bonussystem with the fixed percentage. Therefore\r\n\r\nwe only show the following fields:\r\n- Target for this branch\r\n- Total turnover\r\n- Total bonus\r\n\r\nBonus distributed proportionally to hours worked:\r\nDenise Ramirez - 7.5 hours:  0.00\r\nVanity Weustink - 7.5 hours:  0.00\r\n\r\nSo the bonussystem is according to the old system, based on the percentage of 7,5%.\r\n(We also need to show it, like in the old way)\r\n\r\nAlso in this overview http://www.teamsabon.nl/finance/nettoBonuses we need to do the following:\r\n- Column header \'Netto bonus total\' has to be renamed to \'Netto cash bonus\' (dutch: Netto contante bonus)\r\nWhat values we show: We show here the ammount of bonus wich is calculated with the new bonussystem\r\n\r\n- We need to add column header: \'Netto per bank\'.\r\nWhat values we show: We show here the ammount of bonusses wich are calculated with the old bonussytem (used by V&D shops braches only)\r\n\r\n               \r\n\r\nStep 7 - This step not needed.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe \'V&D shop\' branches also dont have values in the Branch Results module for:\r\n\r\n- Conversion rate\r\n\r\n- Visitors',NULL,NULL,'5','1561','7',NULL,'2684','2','2011-08-04 23:31:49','2011-09-02 21:50:07','2011-08-04','0',NULL,NULL,'25523','1','2','0');
