INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('27972','2','2379','Planning > Agenda: Always remember chosen overview','So if they have chosen in the week overview, some specific week number, it should always remember this for the logged in user. So that next time they come back, it shows the overview like the user left since last time. \r\n\r\nThey especially need this feature, for when they plan in an employer with the employee planning form. On save (button: schedule) it often shows the initial week overview. And not the overview they have set, before performing the planning action.',NULL,'1738','5','1561','5',NULL,'1561','3','2011-08-24 21:35:35','2011-09-08 19:15:49','2011-08-24','0',NULL,NULL,'27972','1','2','0');
INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('27973','2','2379','In branch results overview, for branches who have received a bonus, mark row bg with green color','So in this overview: http://www.teamsabon.nl/finance/branchResults when an branch has received a bonus (so the planned in employers have received a bonus) it should mark the background of the table row with a green color. This is only relevant for \'Day\' and \'Week\' view. Year is not relevant.\r\n\r\nAlso use this green color for table row bg: #CDEB8B',NULL,'1738','5','1561','5',NULL,'1561','5','2011-08-24 21:41:18','2011-09-06 23:17:58','2011-08-24','100',NULL,NULL,'27973','1','2','0');
INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('27976','2','2379','Results overviews: Change decimal notation from . to ,','We need to change in all overviews, for example here http://www.teamsabon.nl/finance/branchResults and http://www.teamsabon.nl/finance/nettoBonuses and on more places, the notation of a decimal. Right now we use everywhere a dot. But we should us an comma instead --> ,\r\n\r\nThis also applies to the excel exports, and the results email\'s sent.',NULL,'1738','5','1561','6',NULL,'1561','8','2011-08-24 21:44:52','2011-09-08 19:35:24','2011-08-24','0',NULL,NULL,'27976','1','2','0');
INSERT INTO `issues` VALUES ('27979','2','2379','Daily results e-mail','Right now the system sends in the morning, the daily results for yesterday. This e-mail must not be send in the morning, but be sended on the same day at 23:00 PM. In other words, at the end of a day, it should send at 23:00 PM a daily results e-mail.\r\n\r\nAlso please take a look at the attached results PDF in those e-mails. It would be great if we could add column/rows dividers (thin lines) so that the overview is better to understand and read.',NULL,'1738','5','1561','6',NULL,'1561','9','2011-08-24 21:58:34','2011-09-08 19:36:37','2011-08-24','100',NULL,NULL,'27979','1','2','0');
