INSERT INTO `journals` VALUES ('19398','10483','Issue','1561','Each client can have:\r\n- several objects (an object is the same as a location)\r\n\r\nEach object (location) can have:\r\n- attached documents, organized into user-created folders\r\n- Forms > Forms have:\r\n  - Fill in date\r\n  - State (incomplete, expired, completed)\r\n  - Several form templates (maybe connected with products)\r\n\r\nEach form template can have:\r\n- several columns. Each column can have:\r\n- header text (label)\r\n- type: checkmark or input value\r\n- Layout of columns/rows can be also created like in the current system (to be flexible).\r\n- start date - start of current form fill\r\n- Frequency: When start next form fill. \r\n  - Next form fill starts independent of previous form fill date (yes, autocreate).\r\n  - Repeats until deleting (yes)\r\n\r\nSeveral assigned users from list of ERP users. Also guest accounts for clients. But probably just another users group with very limited access (yes).\r\n\r\n\r\nInterface (pending)','2011-01-26 19:50:14');
