INSERT INTO `journals` VALUES ('22603','12168','Issue','1561','- Page measures fix\n\n\n\n\n\n\n- The text on the final page from \'Bepalingen\' till \'...verzoek aan u toegestuurd..\' must be editable. Where we can do this?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n- On the first page the adres text in left corner, is now bold. This must be made nomal (regular). Also we have the text line \'T.a.v. <Main contact person>\'. There we use the value \'Dhr.\' or \'Mevr.\'. Indicating if it\'s a gentleman or misses. They want here not to show the short namings but:\n\nT.a.v. de heer <CONTACT> (instead of dhr.)\nT.a.v. mevrouw <CONTACT> (instead of mevr.)\n\nAlso under we have the text:\n_Betreft: offerte < Offer code >\nTer attentie van: < Title > < Main contact person last name >,_\n*We have also the < Title > tag. Here we also replace the shortnames with values from here above.*\n\n\n\n\n\n- Also the text \'BioLab research & solutions B.V.\' is bold now on first page. Make this regular.\n\n\n\n- Everywhere there are enters between lines. Please follow the given template, and remove this lines (i see this when i download pdf and also in doc)\n\n\n\n- Discussed wich contractperiod we must show on top (Contractsduur:). They say that when they make an offer this contractperiod is everywhere the same for the subprojects.\n\n\n\n\n\n- On the other hand, the frequencies of the subprojects can be different. That\'s why the listing on top (Frequentie:) we can remove. Because we basically already show the frequency individually per subproject in the column header \'Aantal bezoeken per jaar\' (ammount of visits per year).\n\n\n\n\n\n- _summary price/tax/discount per year: I take total for all subprojects for all project length and divide on project length_\n*Don\'t really understand. But how must be is: In the price summary on bottom must be just a sum of all subproject totals.*\n\n\n\n\n\n- Client wants to show on bottom only the Total price excluding btw. This means we can remove:\n* 19% BTW:.......\n* Tota